References (Unit 5)
•	Aven, T. & Thekdi, S. (2025). Risk Science. Routledge.
•	Barafort, B., Mesquida, A.L. & Mas, A. (2018). ISO 31000-based integrated risk management process assessment model for IT organisations. Computer Standards & Interfaces, 57, 41–50. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.csi.2017.12.003
•	Kirvan, P. (2021). Top 15 IT security frameworks and standards explained. TechTarget / SearchSecurity. https://www.techtarget.com/searchsecurity/tip/Top-IT-security-frameworks-and-standards
•	Sutton, D. (2021). Information Risk Management, Appendix G.
•	Adhillah, M.N. et al. (2025). ‘Systematic Literature Review: The Development of Enterprise Risk Management’, Jurnal Manajemen Bisnis, Akuntansi dan Keuangan, 4(1), 81–100.
•	Data Protection Commission (2020). Case Studies. https://www.dataprotection.ie/en/dpc-guidance/case-studies

